## DO's and DON'Ts

### ❌ DON'T

```html
<!-- WRONG: Using Bootstrap classes without AdminLTE -->
<button class="btn btn-default">Default</button>

<!-- WRONG: Mixing different button styles inconsistently -->
<button class="btn btn-secondary">Secondary</button>
<button class="btn btn-light">Light</button>  <!-- Hard to see on white background -->

<!-- WRONG: Not using outline for secondary actions -->
<button class="btn btn-danger">Discard</button>  <!-- Looks like a dangerous action -->
```

### ✅ DO

```html
<!-- CORRECT: Use outline for secondary actions -->
<button class="btn btn-outline-dark">Descartar</button>

<!-- CORRECT: Use primary for main action -->
<button class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>

<!-- CORRECT: Use consistent color scheme -->
<button class="btn btn-success">Guardar</button>
<button class="btn btn-outline-dark">Cancelar</button>
```

